Subject: [PATCH RFC v1 1/2] bus: add Wiegand write-only GPIO driver
Date:   Thu, 28 Jul 2022 11:17:11 +0200
Message-Id: <20220728091712.13395-1-m.zatovic1@gmail.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.37.1
